  "detailed_description": "<h1>HAPPY FUN TIME ON DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485670/extras/51ffd0176867072c632ca92acc176a9c.poster.avif?t=1667070812\" width=650 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485670/extras/51ffd0176867072c632ca92acc176a9c.webm?t=1667070812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485670/extras/51ffd0176867072c632ca92acc176a9c.mp4?t=1667070812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Mini Golf Arena</strong> is an exciting multiplayer mini golf game for up to 24 players online. <br>Compete with players from all over the world!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 7 Golf courses with 18 holes (126 holes total).<br></li><li> Full ball customization (Hats, Trails, Models, Colors).<br></li><li> Support Steam Workshop. <br>Build & play custom maps together with your friends.<br></li><li> Support up to 24 players online.<br></li><li> Chat & voice chat support.<br></li><li> Unique gaming experience.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485670/extras/a6b131842144627a2a6f2d118893195e.avif?t=1667070812\" width=600 height=128 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485670/extras/51ffd0176867072c632ca92acc176a9c.poster.avif?t=1667070812\" width=650 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485670/extras/51ffd0176867072c632ca92acc176a9c.webm?t=1667070812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485670/extras/51ffd0176867072c632ca92acc176a9c.mp4?t=1667070812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Mini Golf Arena</strong> is an exciting multiplayer mini golf game for up to 24 players online. <br>Compete with players from all over the world!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 7 Golf courses with 18 holes (126 holes total).<br></li><li> Full ball customization (Hats, Trails, Models, Colors).<br></li><li> Support Steam Workshop. <br>Build & play custom maps together with your friends.<br></li><li> Support up to 24 players online.<br></li><li> Chat & voice chat support.<br></li><li> Unique gaming experience.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485670/extras/a6b131842144627a2a6f2d118893195e.avif?t=1667070812\" width=600 height=128 /></span>",
